ching</Choice><Choice>will catching</Choice></Dropdown>the five o'clock train.<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">8<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>We <Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">'re having</Choice><Choice>'re have</Choice><Choice>are going to have</Choice></Dropdown>a party on Saturday. Would you like to come?<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">9<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>What<Dropdown><Choice>will you doing</Choice><Choice>do you doing</Choice><Choice is-correct="1">are you doing</Choice></Dropdown>this evening? Nothing much.<br></br><PersonName><font face="Verdana" size="12" color="#000000">10<TAB></TAB></font></PersonName>Have a great holiday. Thanks, I <Dropdown><Choice is-correct="1">'ll send</Choice><Choice>'m going to send</Choice><Choice>'m sending</Choice></Dropdown>you a postcard! </ContentGapFillDropdown></GapFillDropdown></Activity></Entry></CD-RAT>